00:02:10.366 --> 00:02:13.325
Fortunately, Metasploit
is well-thought-out

00:02:13.325 --> 00:02:16.900
and offers a unified
and sensible interface.

00:02:18.016 --> 00:02:22.275
In this module, we will provide a
walkthrough of the Metasploit Framework,

00:02:22.275 --> 00:02:28.866
